title: FK OEZ Letohrad
text:
FK OEZ Letohrad is a <a href="association%20football">football</a> club located in <a href="Letohrad">Letohrad</a>, <a href="Czech%20Republic">Czech Republic</a>. It currently plays in Divize C, which is in the <a href="Czech%20Fourth%20Division">Czech Fourth Division</a>.
The club was promoted from the <a href="Czech%20Fourth%20Division">Czech Fourth Division</a> in 2011.
